/-- CHI-254 byte-pin (severity-1 gap from project memory closed).
    `committedJsonBytes` is a literal copy of what ships in
    `maps/humanoid_bones_map.json`. `genJson` is computed from the
    Lean spec. `native_decide` evaluates byte-equality at compile
    time, so any drift between the spec, the literal, or the
    shipping file fails the Lake build. -/
theorem committedJsonBytes_matches_genJson :
    committedJsonBytes = genJson := by native_decide

